text: Roberto Muñoz (born 14 October 1955) is a Chilean former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race and the points race events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Chile Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Pan American Games medalists in cycling Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Chile Category:Cyclists at the 1979 Pan American Games
